{"tid":1492921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸律師陳秋實 其實拍片係曲線叫大家唔好割蓆","createTime":"2019-08-21T04:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T05:12:27.000Z","uid":99856,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e19081938a02554cc74a1f5aeabcf9cf0b8a616","tid":1492921,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2225543547590119?s=100000236490351&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2225543547590119%3Fs%3D100000236490351%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=6de310ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2225543547590119?s=100000236490351&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n佢有條片係介紹3個名詞 和理非 勇武 不割蓆 仲解釋得清楚過和理非同勇武自己 專登擺呢3隻字一齊講個訊息已經好簡單<br />\n就係和理非 勇武 不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇番其他片 佢係知道咩事而且知道得比某d香港人更加清楚<br />\n<br />\n佢黎香港唔係想著草 所以冇直接講香港加油之類<br />\n但佢818都陪左香港人全日<br />\n<br />\n用自己生命換取呢幾條片<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好辜負佢 一齊走落去好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2da8439649f5b125ce75697e88b2653fe23c1f","tid":1492921,"uid":41005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RGmWlU2EPF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRGmWlU2EPF4&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41FpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=336a7af1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RGmWlU2EPF4</a>"},{"pid":"5de423ea8280192b3d69e4be20b466a311706309","tid":1492921,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebab9e11066a00813786e43b8bcf799e8582d3c5","tid":1492921,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:58:52.00